Investor Relations Home
















HomeHome  >  Investor Relations




        Investor Relations Home
    




Myers Industries is traded on the New York Stock Exchange under the symbol MYE and reports operations in two core segments: Material Handling and Distribution.  In the Material Handling Segment, we concentrate on the manufacturing of polymer products for storing and transporting a broad range of materials and goods.  In the Distribution Segment, our core business centers on the global distribution of tire repair and retread products.
As a current or perspective shareholder of Myers Industries, we want you to feel confident that you will see a return on the investment you make in our business.
Why should you invest in Myers Industries? 

Significant progress in streamlining business
    
Enhanced platform to accelerate growth
    
Strong market positions; plans to further penetrate
    expansion markets
    
Financially strong; disciplined capital deployment
    
